Let’s grow those shoulders!! Go heavy, breath in through your nose and out through your mouth. 
Rest 30 seconds between...
body:
Let’s grow those shoulders!! Go heavy, breath in through your nose and out through your mouth.

Rest 30 seconds between exercises and 90 seconds between sets.

Superset #1

Military barbell press — 3 sets x 10 reps

Lateral raises — 3 sets x 10 reps

Superset #2

Dumbbell shoulder press — 3 sets x 10 reps

Front raises — 3 sets x 10 reps

Superset #3

Upright barbell row — 3 sets x 10 reps

Bent over rear delt raise — 3 sets x 10 reps

title: Brie Larson quiere protagonizar una película de Metroid
body:
Brie Larson está lista para asumir el papel principal de Samus Aran, en caso de que una película de Metroid obtenga luz verde. La actriz de Captain Marvel se puso un disfraz de Samus Aran para Halloween. El traje de Larson provocó reacciones de los fanáticos de Metroid en todas partes, quienes comenzaron a especular sobre […]
